data.description: Welcome to this charming two-bedroom, two-bathroom home situated on a desirable double lot with the option to build on the second lot. Located on a corner lot in Palmetto, this property offers plenty of space and potential for expansion or customization to fit your needs. As you approach the home, you'll be greeted by an inviting screened-in front porch, the perfect spot to relax and enjoy the Florida breeze. The spacious porch provides a cozy and private outdoor space where you can sip your morning coffee or unwind in the evenings. Boat and RV enthusiasts will be delighted to know that parking for your recreational vehicles is allowed on the property, providing convenience and flexibility for those who love to explore the great outdoors. Step inside and be welcomed by a light and bright interior, filled with natural sunlight that illuminates the open floor plan. The well-designed layout creates a seamless flow between the living spaces, perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen is a standout feature of this home, boasting granite countertops, a range with a hood, and plenty of kitchen cabinets for ample storage. Whether you're a seasoned chef or simply enjoy cooking, this kitchen offers both style and functionality to meet all your culinary needs. The living room is enhanced with a ceiling fan, ensuring a comfortable and breezy atmosphere all year round. This space is perfect for relaxation and gathering with family and friends. With its double lot, this property provides an abundance of outdoor space to enjoy the beautiful Florida weather. Whether you envision a lush garden, a pool oasis, or additional structures, the possibilities are endless. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours. With its convenient location, double lot potential, and charming features, it's the perfect place to create lasting memories. Schedule your showing today and seize the chance to embrace the Florida lifestyle at its finest
